skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my tarot
des: Say, "Alexa, open My Tarot" any time, and she'll read a randomly-selected card. You can ask for a tarot card as often as you want; there are no limits! There are many ways to read a card, and different nuances to each, so the readings will always stay true to the core meanings, but be updated for fresh content often.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
